description: The fund will normally invest at least 90% of its net assets (including investment borrowings) in the common stocks and depositary receipts that comprise the index. The index is modified market cap weighted based on free float market capitalization and includes the securities of real estate companies or REITs that are publicly traded on an official stock exchange located in North America, Europe or Asia and provides an audited annual report in English.
name: First Trust FTSE EPRA/NAREIT Developed Markets Real Estate Index Fund
